   547→/**
   548→ * Props for the Widget wrapper component
   549→ *
   550→ * Widgets are the primary dashboard building blocks. Each widget
   551→ * displays in a card with optional header, drag controls, and
   552→ * built-in loading/error state handling.
   553→ *
   554→ * @example
   555→ * ```tsx
   556→ * <Widget
   557→ *   id="weather"
   558→ *   title="Weather"
   559→ *   category="Information"
   560→ *   loading={isLoading}
   561→ *   error={fetchError}
   562→ *   onRefresh={refetch}
   563→ * >
   564→ *   <WeatherDisplay data={weatherData} />
   565→ * </Widget>
   566→ * ```
